measureDetails.title: AIS_HEDIS_2020
measureDetails.description: The percentage of members 19 years of age and older who are up-to-date on recommended routine vaccines for influenza, tetanus and diphtheria (Td) or tetanus, diphtheria and acellular pertussis (Tdap), zoster and pneumococcal.

measureDetails.recommendations: The Advisory Committee on Immunization Practices recommends annual influenza vaccination; and tetanus, diphtheria and acellular pertussis (Tdap) and/or tetanus and diphtheria (Td) vaccine; herpes zoster vaccine; and the 13-valent pneumococcal conjugate vaccine (PCV13) and the 23-valent pneumococcal polysaccharide vaccine (PPSV23) for adults at various ages.
measureDetails.improvementNotations: A higher score indicates better performance

measureDetails.definitions:
Participation: The identifiers and descriptors for each organization’s coverage used to define members’ eligibility for measure reporting. Allocation for reporting is based on eligibility during the Participation Period.
Participation Period: The Measurement Period.
measureDetails.guidance:
HEDIS ECDS technical specifications include both narrative specification language and expression of the measure logic in Clinical Quality Language (CQL)-based Health Quality Measure Format (HQMF), Release 1. At this time the measure logic is provided as a reference, complementing the narrative measure calculation.
Allocation: The member was enrolled with a medical benefit throughout the participation period.
Requirements: The composite is based on a model that looks at the number of immunizations that were administered or contraindicated due to history of anaphylactic reaction or encephalopathy following vaccination (numerator) out of the possible number of immunizations needed to be administered to members, per clinical guideline recommendations for the age group (denominator).
For commercial and Medicaid plan members 19–65 years of age, Denominator 5 is determined by summing Denominators 1–3. Numerator 5 is determined by summing Numerators 1–3.
For Medicare plan members 66 years of age and older, Denominator 5 is determined by summing Denominators 1–4. Numerator 5 is determined by summing Numerators 1–4.
measureDetails.initialPopDescription:
Initial Population 1: Members 19 years of age and older at the start of the Measurement Period who also meet the criteria for Participation.
Initial Population 2: Same as the Initial Population 1.
Initial Population 3: Members 50 years and older at the start of Measurement Period who also meet the criteria for Participation.
Initial Population 4: Members 66 years and older at the start of the Measurement Period who also meet the criteria for Participation.
measureDetails.denominatorDescription:
Denominator 1: The Initial Population 1, minus Exclusions.
Denominator 2: Same as Denominator 1.
Denominator 3: The Initial Population 3, minus Exclusions.
Denominator 4: The Initial Population 4, minus Exclusions.
measureDetails.denominatorExclusionsDescription: Exclude members with any of the following: • Active chemotherapy any time during the Measurement Period. • Bone marrow transplant any time during the Measurement Period. • History of immunocompromising conditions, cochlear implants, anatomic or functional asplenia, sickle cell anemia and HB-S disease or cerebrospinal fluid leaks any time during the member’s history through the end of the Measurement Period. • In hospice or using hospice services during the Measurement Period
measureDetails.numeratorDescription:
Numerator 1: Members in Denominator 1 who received an influenza vaccine on or between July 1 of the year prior to the Measurement Period and June 30 of the Measurement Period, or who had a prior influenza virus vaccine adverse reaction any time before or during the Measurement Period.
Numerator 2: Members in Denominator 2 who received at least one Td vaccine or one Tdap vaccine between nine years prior to the start of the Measurement Period and the end of the Measurement Period, OR Members in Denominator 2 with history of at least one of the following contraindications any time before or during the Measurement Period: • Anaphylaxis due to Tdap vaccine, anaphylaxis due to Td vaccine or its components. • Encephalopathy due to Tdap or Td vaccination (post-tetanus vaccination encephalitis, post-diphtheria vaccination encephalitis, post-pertussis vaccination encephalitis).
Numerator 3: Members in Denominator 3 who received at least one dose of the herpes zoster live vaccine or two doses of the herpes zoster recombinant vaccine at least 28 days apart, any time on or after the member’s 50th birthday before or during the Measurement Period, or who had a prior adverse reaction caused by zoster vaccine or its components any time before or during the Measurement Period.
Numerator 4: Members in Denominator 4 who were administered both the 13-valent pneumococcal conjugate vaccine and the 23-valent pneumococcal polysaccharide vaccine at least 12 months apart, with the first occurrence after the age of 60 before or during the Measurement Period, or prior pneumococcal vaccine adverse reaction any time before or during the Measurement Period.

definition.name: Stratification 1
definition.logic: exists ( ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate": "Birth date"] BirthDate where Common."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")between 19 and 65 ) and Common."Product Line"("Product Line", end of "Measurement Period", "Measurement Period" )= Common."Commercial Product"

definition.name: Stratification 3
Stratification 2
definition.logic: exists ( ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate": "Birth date"] BirthDate where Common."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")between 19 and 65 ) and Common."Product Line"("Product Line", end of "Measurement Period", "Measurement Period" )= Common."Medicaid Product"

definition.name: Enrolled During Participation Period
Herpes Zoster Live Vaccine After Age 50 Before End of Measurement Period
Herpes Zoster Recombinant Vaccine After Age 50 Before End of Measurement Period
definition.logic: ( ( ["Immunization, Administered": "Herpes Zoster Recombinant Immunization"] union ( ["Procedure, Performed": "Herpes Zoster Recombinant Vaccine Procedure"] ZosterRecombinantProcedure return "Immunization, Administered" { authorDatetime: start of ZosterRecombinantProcedure.relevantPeriod } ) ) ZosterRecombinant with ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate": "Birth date"] BirthDate such that Common."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, ZosterRecombinant.authorDatetime)>= 50 ) ZosterRecombinantAge50 where ZosterRecombinantAge50.authorDatetime on or before end of "Measurement Period"

definition.name: Numerator 1
Numerator 4
definition.logic: "Pneumococcal Vaccines Administered After Age 60 Before End of Measurement Period" or "Pneumococcal Vaccine Adverse Reaction Before End of Measurement Period"

definition.name: Numerator 3
definition.logic: "Herpes Zoster Live Vaccine After Age 50 Before End of Measurement Period" or "Two Doses of Recombinant Zoster Vaccine 28 Days Apart After Age 50 Before End of Measurement Period" or "Adverse Reaction Caused by Zoster Vaccine Before End of Measurement Period"

definition.name: Tdap or Td Vaccine Administered Within 9 Years prior to Measurement Period
Numerator 2
definition.logic: "Tdap or Td Vaccine Administered Within 9 Years prior to Measurement Period" or "Anaphylaxis Due to Td Vaccine Before End of Measurement Period" or "Anaphylaxis Due to Tdap Vaccine Before End of Measurement Period" or "Post Tetanus Vaccination Encephalitis Before End of Measurement Period" or "Post Diphtheria Vaccination Encephalitis Before End of Measurement Period" or "Post Pertussis Vaccination Encephalitis Before End of Measurement Period"

definition.name: Denominator 1
definition.logic: "Initial Population 1"

definition.name: Denominator 2
definition.logic: "Initial Population 2"

definition.name: Denominator 3
definition.logic: "Initial Population 3"

definition.name: Denominator 4
definition.logic: "Initial Population 4"

definition.name: Exclusions
definition.logic: exists ( ( ["Procedure, Performed": "Chemotherapy Procedure"] union ["Encounter, Performed": "Chemotherapy Encounter"] ) Chemotherapy where Chemotherapy.relevantPeriod overlaps "Measurement Period" ) or exists ( ["Procedure, Performed": "Bone Marrow Transplant"] BoneMarrowTransplant where BoneMarrowTransplant.relevantPeriod overlaps "Measurement Period" ) or exists ( ( ["Diagnosis": "Immunocompromising Conditions"] union ["Diagnosis": "Cochlear Implant Diagnosis"] union ["Diagnosis": "Anatomic or Functional Asplenia"] union ["Diagnosis": "Cerebrospinal Fluid Leak"] union ["Diagnosis": "Sickle Cell Anemia and HB S Disease"] ) ExclusionDiagnoses where ExclusionDiagnoses.prevalencePeriod starts on or before end of "Measurement Period" ) or exists ( ["Procedure, Performed": "Cochlear Implant"] CochlearImplantProcedure where CochlearImplantProcedure.relevantPeriod starts on or before end of "Measurement Period" ) or exists ( ["Device, Applied": "Cochlear Implant Device"] CochlearImplantDevice where CochlearImplantDevice.relevantPeriod starts on or before end of "Measurement Period" ) or exists Common."Hospice Intervention or Encounter"

definition.name: Pneumococcal Polysaccharide Vaccine 23 After Age 60 Before End of Measurement Period
definition.logic: ( ( ["Immunization, Administered": "Pneumococcal Polysaccharide 23 Immunization"] union ( ["Procedure, Performed": "Pneumococcal Polysaccharide 23 Vaccine Procedure"] PPSV23Procedure return "Immunization, Administered" { authorDatetime: start of PPSV23Procedure.relevantPeriod } ) ) PPSV23 with ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] BirthDate such that Common."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, PPSV23.authorDatetime)>= 60 ) PPSV2360 where PPSV2360.authorDatetime on or before end of "Measurement Period"

definition.name: Pneumococcal Conjugate Vaccine 13 After Age 60 Before End of Measurement Period
definition.logic: ( ( ["Immunization, Administered": "Pneumococcal Conjugate 13 Immunization"] union ( ["Procedure, Performed": "Pneumococcal Conjugate 13 Vaccine Procedure"] PCV13Procedure return "Immunization, Administered" { authorDatetime: start of PCV13Procedure.relevantPeriod } ) ) PCV13 with ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate": "Birth date"] BirthDate such that Common."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, PCV13.authorDatetime)>= 60 ) PCV1360 where PCV1360.authorDatetime on or before end of "Measurement Period"

definition.name: Pneumococcal Vaccine Adverse Reaction Before End of Measurement Period
definition.logic: exists ["Diagnosis": "Pneumococcal vaccine adverse reaction (disorder)"] PneumoAdverseRXN where PneumoAdverseRXN.prevalencePeriod starts on or before end of "Measurement Period"

definition.name: Pneumococcal Vaccines Administered After Age 60 Before End of Measurement Period
definition.logic: exists "Pneumococcal Conjugate Vaccine 13 After Age 60 Before End of Measurement Period" PCV13 with "Pneumococcal Polysaccharide Vaccine 23 After Age 60 Before End of Measurement Period" PPSV23 such that months between PCV13.authorDatetime and PPSV23.authorDatetime >= 12 or months between PPSV23.authorDatetime and PCV13.authorDatetime >= 12

definition.name: Post Diphtheria Vaccination Encephalitis Before End of Measurement Period
definition.logic: exists ["Diagnosis": "Post diphtheria vaccination encephalitis (disorder)"] DiphtheriaEncephalitis where DiphtheriaEncephalitis.prevalencePeriod starts on or before end of "Measurement Period"

definition.name: Post Pertussis Vaccination Encephalitis Before End of Measurement Period
definition.logic: exists ["Diagnosis": "Post pertussis vaccination encephalitis (disorder)"] PertussisEncephalitis where PertussisEncephalitis.prevalencePeriod starts on or before end of "Measurement Period"

definition.name: Post Tetanus Vaccination Encephalitis Before End of Measurement Period
definition.logic: exists ["Diagnosis": "Post tetanus vaccination encephalitis (disorder)"] TetanusEncephalitis where TetanusEncephalitis.prevalencePeriod starts on or before end of "Measurement Period"

definition.name: Two Doses of Recombinant Zoster Vaccine 28 Days Apart After Age 50 Before End of Measurement Period
definition.logic: exists "Herpes Zoster Recombinant Vaccine After Age 50 Before End of Measurement Period" Recombinant1 with "Herpes Zoster Recombinant Vaccine After Age 50 Before End of Measurement Period" Recombinant2 such that days between Recombinant1.authorDatetime and Recombinant2.authorDatetime >= 28

definition.name: Influenza Virus Vaccine Adverse Reaction Before End of Measurement Period
definition.logic: exists ["Diagnosis": "Influenza virus vaccine adverse reaction (disorder)"] FluAdverseRXN where FluAdverseRXN.prevalencePeriod starts on or before end of "Measurement Period"

definition.name: Anaphylaxis Due to Td Vaccine Before End of Measurement Period
definition.logic: exists ["Diagnosis": "Anaphylaxis due to diphtheria and tetanus vaccine (disorder)"] AnaphylaxisTd where AnaphylaxisTd.prevalencePeriod starts on or before end of "Measurement Period"

definition.name: Adverse Reaction Caused by Zoster Vaccine Before End of Measurement Period
definition.logic: exists ["Diagnosis": "Adverse reaction caused by zoster vaccine (disorder)"] AdverseRXNZoster where AdverseRXNZoster.prevalencePeriod starts on or before end of "Measurement Period"

definition.name: Initial Population 1
definition.logic: exists ( ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate": "Birth date"] BirthDate where Common."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")>= 19 ) and "Enrolled During Participation Period"

definition.name: Initial Population 2
definition.logic: exists ( ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate": "Birth date"] BirthDate where Common."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")>= 19 ) and "Enrolled During Participation Period"

definition.name: Initial Population 3
definition.logic: exists ( ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate": "Birth date"] BirthDate where Common."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")>= 50 ) and "Enrolled During Participation Period"

definition.name: Initial Population 4
definition.logic: exists ( ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate": "Birth date"] BirthDate where Common."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")>= 66 ) and "Enrolled During Participation Period"

definition.name: Anaphylaxis Due to Tdap Vaccine Before End of Measurement Period
definition.logic: exists ["Diagnosis": "Anaphylaxis due to tetanus, diphtheria and acellular pertussis vaccine (disorder)"] AnaphylaxisTdap where AnaphylaxisTdap.prevalencePeriod starts on or before end of "Measurement Period"
